summary: This mod add a female nord assassin Yana to skyrim.She can be found in Whiterun Bannered Mare Inn.
descriptionHtml:
==================================================================================
This is my first follower mod a NordFemale Assassin named Yana she can be found in Whiterun BanneredMare Inn.
Requirments:(highly recommaded)
Hair packs of Fallout3 (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=17993)
Calientes Female Body (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666) or any other body mod you like
Better Females by Bella (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2812)
Flans Eyes for Skyrim (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=14539&navtag=file/images.php?id=14539&tab=3)
Optional Mods:
Better Females by Bella makeup version 1 and no shine.
Joseph Anthonys Lip Gloss for Better Females (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=13860&navtag=file/images.php?id=13860&tab=3)
Nightshade Armor (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=12070&navtag=file/images.php?id=12070&tab=3) or she will appear naked.
CBBE skin texture V2 V3 (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=6554)
================================================================
Instalation.
Unpack the archive to your Skyrim Datafolder,open skyrim launcher Data Files and check Yana.esp.
Unistall.
Delete Yana.esp and Yana.bsa
================================================================
Credits: all respective owners who created the mods.
